  </div>
  <div id="our-expertise" class="flex-1 space-y-4 ~px-4/16 py-8 xl:py-24">
    <h5 class="text-center xl:text-left">Our Expertise</h5>
    <ul class="list-disc list-outside text-muted-foreground ~pl-4/8">
      <li>Innovative product and supply chain solutions</li>
      <li>Cost controls and timeline management</li>
      <li>Quality Control</li>
